{"lemma":"حَمَلاتٌ","slug":"حَمَلاتٌ","root":"ح.م.ل","root_slug":"ح-م-ل","root_link":"/words/roots/ح-م-ل","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":5},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n9160","n9173","n9174","n9175"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%AD%D9%8E%D9%85%D9%8E%D9%84%D8%A7%D8%AA%D9%8C"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of حَمَلَ (ḥamala, “to attack”) (form I)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"attack","examples":[{"text":"شَنَّ الْجَيْشُ حَمْلَةً عَسْكَرِيَّةً عَلَى مَوَاقِعِ الْعَدُوِّ","english":"The army launched a military attack on the enemy's positions."}]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"offensive","tags":["offensive"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"campaign, expedition"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"an organization or a trip arranged by said organization which takes multiple people to travel to a destination, usually with added services such as guides and meals","tags":["Arabic","Modern","Standard"]}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Instance noun from حَمَلَ (ḥamala, “to attack”)."},"ipa":["/ħam.la/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n9160","headword_ar":"حَمَلَهُ","root":"Hml","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HamolN","text_ar":"حَمْلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Mgh, Msb, K, &c., in some copies of the S"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HimolN","text_ar":"حِمْلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":") and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HumolaAnN","text_ar":"حُمْلَانٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Mgh, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He bore it, carried it, took it up and carried it, conveyed it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"carried it off"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"away,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(MA,)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EalaY Zahorihi","text_ar":"عَلَى ظَهْرِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, MA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"upon his back,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EalaY raA^osihi","text_ar":"عَلَى رَاْسِهِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"upon his head;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(MA;) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AHtmlhu","text_ar":"احتملهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies the same: (Msb, K:) or the latter is used in relation to an object inconsiderable and small in comparison with that in relation to which the former is used; as in the saying of En-Nábighah, (TA,)"},{"kind":"quote","text":"A_in~aA A@qotasamonaA xuT~atayonaA bayonanaA\n                      \n                     \n                        fajaAri ↓ \n      faHamalota bar~apa waA@Hotamalotu"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Verily we have divided our two qualities between us, and thou hast borne"},{"kind":"text","text":"as thy share"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"goodness, and I have borne"},{"kind":"text","text":"as my share"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"wickedness"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA * in the present art., and S and TA &c. in arts."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"br","text_ar":"بر"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fjr","text_ar":"فجر"},{"kind":"text","text":".) Hence, in the Kur [xx. 100],"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faA_in~ahu","text_ar":"فَاـِنَّهُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yaHomilu yawoma AlqiyaAmapi wizorFA","text_ar":"يَحْمِلُ يَوْمَ القِيَامَةِ وِزْرًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He shall bear, on the day of resurrection, a heavy burden"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) Hence also, in the Kur [vii. 189],"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hamalato HamolFA xafiyfFA","text_ar":"حَمَلَتْ حَمْلًا خَفِيفًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"She bore a light burden"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; (S, TA;) i. e., [as some say,] the seminal fluid. (TA.) Hence also, in the Kur [xxix. 60],"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wakaA^ay~ino mino daAb~apK laA taHomilu","text_ar":"وَكَاَيِّنْ مِنْ دَابَّةٍ لَا تَحْمِلُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rizoqahaA","text_ar":"رِزْقَهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"And how many a beast"},{"kind":"text","text":"is there that"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"does not bear its sustenance !"},{"kind":"text","text":"], meaning, (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"does not provide its sustenance,"},{"kind":"text","text":"but is sustained by God. (TA.)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yaHomilu AlHaTaba","text_ar":"يَحْمِلُ الحَطَبَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[lit."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He carries firewood"},{"kind":"text","text":"],"},{"kind":"page_break","n":647},{"kind":"text","text":"(A in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HTb","text_ar":"حطب"},{"kind":"text","text":",) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlHaTaba Alr~aToba","text_ar":"الحَطَبَ الرَّطْبَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"juicy,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fresh, firewood"},{"kind":"text","text":"], (Er-Rághib, TA,) means (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he goes about with calumny,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"slander."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HTb","text_ar":"حطب"},{"kind":"text","text":", and Er-Rághib * and TA. *) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hamalahu EalaY","text_ar":"حَمَلَهُ عَلَى"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ald~aAb~ap","text_ar":"الدَّابَّة"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb, TA,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HamolN","text_ar":"حَمْلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb, TA,) ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He carried him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"mounted him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(namely, a man, Msb)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"upon the beast;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AHtmlhu","text_ar":"احتملهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":".] And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hamalahu","text_ar":"حَمَلَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[alone]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He gave him a beast upon which to ride."},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, TA. [See Kur ix. 93.])"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aHomalahu","text_ar":"اَحْمَلَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is not used in this sense. (T, TA.) ―         -b3-  See also 4. ―         -b4-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hamalati AlmaroA^apu","text_ar":"حَمَلَتِ المَرْاَةُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HamolN","text_ar":"حَمْلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,) (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The woman became pregnant,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"conceived:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA:) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hamalato waladahaA","text_ar":"حَمَلَتْ وَلَدَهَا"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"She became pregnant with,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"conceived, her child:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb:) one should not say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hamalato bihi","text_ar":"حَمَلَتْ بِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; or this is rare; (K;) or one should not say this, but it is frequently said; (IJ, TA;) [for] as"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hamalato","text_ar":"حَمَلَتْ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is syn. with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ealiqato","text_ar":"عَلِقَتْ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb, TA,) and the latter is trans. by means of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bi","text_ar":"بِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"the former is thus made trans., (TA,) therefore one says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hamalato bihi fiY layolapi","text_ar":"حَمَلَتْ بِهِ فِى لَيْلَةِ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ka*aA wafiY mawoDiEi ka*aA","text_ar":"كَذَا وَفِى مَوْضِعِ كَذَا"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"She became pregnant with him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"conceived him, in such a night, and in such a place."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb.)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hamalato","text_ar":"حَمَلَتْ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is also said of a ewe or she-goat, and of a female beast of prey, [and app. of any female,] accord. to IAar; meaning (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"She was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, in the first stage of pregnancy."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b5-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hamalati Al$~ajarapu","text_ar":"حَمَلَتِ الشَّجَرَةُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HamolN","text_ar":"حَمْلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The tree"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"bore,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"produced,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"put forth, its fruit."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb.) ―         -b6-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hamala bidayonK","text_ar":"حَمَلَ بِدَيْنٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bidiyapK","text_ar":"بِدِيَةٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HamaAlapN","text_ar":"حَمَالَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (assumed tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He bore,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"took upon himself, the responsibility,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, responsible, for a debt,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a bloodwit:"},{"kind":"text","text":"] (Msb:) [for]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hamala bihi","text_ar":"حَمَلَ بِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HamaAlapN","text_ar":"حَمَالَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", signifies"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kafala","text_ar":"كَفَلَ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S, * K.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hamala AlHamaAlapa","text_ar":"حَمَلَ الحَمَالَةَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tHm~lhA","text_ar":"تحمّلها","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, responsible for the bloodwit,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"debt"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the like"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: both signify the same: (S, TA:) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bihi","text_ar":"بِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tHm~l","text_ar":"تحمّل","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He took it upon himself,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became responsible,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"answerable, for it:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kfl","text_ar":"كفل"},{"kind":"text","text":":) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"muEoZamahu","text_ar":"مُعْظَمَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tHm~l","text_ar":"تحمّل","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He took,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"imposed, upon himself,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"undertook, the main part of it:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Jel in xxiv. 11:) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlA^amora","text_ar":"الاَمْرَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AHtml","text_ar":"احتمل","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He took,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"imposed, upon himself,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"undertook, the thing,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"affair; he bore,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"took upon himself, the burden thereof."},{"kind":"text","text":"(L in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qld","text_ar":"قلد"},{"kind":"text","text":".) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hamala qawomN Eano qawomK diyapF","text_ar":"حَمَلَ قَوْمٌ عَنْ قَوْمٍ دِيَةً"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K, TA,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"garaAmapF","text_ar":"غَرَامَةً"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,) (assumed tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A party bore,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"took upon itself, for a party, the responsibility for a bloodwit,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a debt"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the like;"},{"kind":"text","text":"] as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tHm~l","text_ar":"تحمّل","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S.) [And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hamala","text_ar":"حَمَلَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eano fulaAnK lifulaAnK ka*aA","text_ar":"عَنْ فُلَانٍ لِفُلَانٍ كَذَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He bore,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"took upon himself, for such a one, the responsibility, to such a one, for such a thing."},{"kind":"text","text":"] And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HamaAlapF bayona","text_ar":"حَمَالَةً بَيْنَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tHm~l","text_ar":"تحمّل","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qawomK","text_ar":"قَوْمٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He bore,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"took upon himself, the responsibility for the bloodwits between people,"},{"kind":"text","text":"in order to make peace between them, when war had occurred between them, and men's blood had been shed. (TA, from a trad.) ―         -b7-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hamala ZulomFA","text_ar":"حَمَلَ ظُلْمًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He made himself chargeable with wrongdoing"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (Kur xx. 110.) ―         -b8-  ["},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hamala AlA^amaAnapa","text_ar":"حَمَلَ الاَمَانَةَ"},{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^amaAnapN","text_ar":"اَمَانَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": accord. to some, it means (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He took upon himself,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"accepted, the trust:"},{"kind":"text","text":"accord. to others,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he was unfaithful to it:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AiHotamalahaA","text_ar":"اِحْتَمَلَهَا","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"means the same.] ―         -b9-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hamalotu A_idolaAlahu","text_ar":"حَمَلْتُ اـِدْلَالَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":": see 8. ―         -b10-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hamala Eanohu","text_ar":"حَمَلَ عَنْهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":": see 8. ―         -b11-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hamala fulaAnN AlHiqoda EalaY fulaAnK","text_ar":"حَمَلَ فُلَانٌ الحِقْدَ عَلَى فُلَانٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Such a one"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"bore"},{"kind":"text","text":"or]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"concealed in his mind rancour, malevolence, malice,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"spite, against such a one."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fulaAnN laA yaHomilu","text_ar":"فُلَانٌ لَا يَحْمِلُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", i. e."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yuZohiru gaDabahu","text_ar":"يُظْهِرُ غَضَبَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[which may be meant as the explanation of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lA yHml","text_ar":"لا يحمل"},{"kind":"text","text":", i. e. (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Such a one shows"},{"kind":"text","text":"(or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"will not conceal"},{"kind":"text","text":")"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"his anger;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and thus SM understood it; or as the explanation of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yHml","text_ar":"يحمل"},{"kind":"text","text":"alone, i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"such a one will not show his anger"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (Az, TA:) [for]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hamala AlgaDaba","text_ar":"حَمَلَ الغَضَبَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HamolN","text_ar":"حَمْلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,) means (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he showed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"manifested, anger."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA.) And hence, it is said, is the saying, in a trad.,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_i*aA balaga AlmaA='u qul~atayoni","text_ar":"اـِذَا بَلَغَ المَا=ءُ قُلَّتَيْنِ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lamo yaHomilo xabavFA","text_ar":"لَمْ يَحْمِلْ خَبَثًا"},{"kind":"text","text":", i. e. (assumed tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"When the water amounts to"},{"kind":"text","text":"the quantity of"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"two vessels of the kind called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qul~ap","text_ar":"قُلَّة"},{"kind":"text","text":",]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"impurity does not appear in it:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, K, * TA:) or the meaning is, (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it does not admit the bearing of impurity:"},{"kind":"text","text":"for one says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fulaAnN laA yaHomilu","text_ar":"فُلَانٌ لَا يَحْمِلُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlD~ayoma","text_ar":"الضَّيْمَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", i. e. (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"such a one refuses to bear,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"submit to, and repels from himself, injury."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb.) You say also,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hamala mino *`lika A^anafFA","text_ar":"حَمَلَ مِنْ ذٰلِكَ اَنَفًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He conceived, in consequence of that, disdain,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"scorn, arising from indignation and anger."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Anf","text_ar":"انف"},{"kind":"text","text":", from a trad.) ―         -b12-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hamala AlHadiyva","text_ar":"حَمَلَ الحَدِيثَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He bore in his memory, knowing by heart, the tradition,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"narrative,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"story;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and in like manner,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlquroA=na","text_ar":"القُرْا=نَ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the Kur-án"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (Msb in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rwY","text_ar":"روى"},{"kind":"text","text":".) ―         -b13-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hamala fulaAnFA","text_ar":"حَمَلَ فُلَانًا"},{"kind":"text","text":", and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bihi","text_ar":"بِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tHm~l","text_ar":"تحمّل","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ealayohi","text_ar":"عَلَيْهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He relied upon such a one"},{"kind":"text","text":"in intercession, and in a case of need. (TA.) ―         -b14-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Humila EalaY Aln~aAqapi","text_ar":"حُمِلَ عَلَى النَّاقَةِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The she-camel was covered by a stallion."},{"kind":"text","text":"(M in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Smd","text_ar":"صمد"},{"kind":"text","text":".) ―         -b15-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hamala Ealyohi","text_ar":"حَمَلَ عَليْهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[as syn. with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ham~alahu","text_ar":"حَمَّلَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: see 2, in three places. ―         -b16-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hamala","text_ar":"حَمَلَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EalaY daAb~atihi fawoqa TaAqatihaA fiY Als~ayori","text_ar":"عَلَى دَابَّتِهِ فَوْقَ طَاقَتِهَا فِى السَّيْرِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He tasked his beast beyond its power in journeying,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"marching,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in respect of pace"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (S in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jhd","text_ar":"جهد"},{"kind":"text","text":".) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hamala EalaY nafosihi fiY Als~ayori","text_ar":"حَمَلَ عَلَى نَفْسِهِ فِى السَّيْرِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He jaded,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fatigued, himself,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"tasked himself beyond his power, in journeying,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"marching."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, TA.) [See also 6.] ―         -b17-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hamala Ealayohi fiY AlHarobi","text_ar":"حَمَلَ عَلَيْهِ فِى الحَرْبِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HamolapN","text_ar":"حَمْلَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[which is properly an inf. n. of un.], (T, S,) (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He charged,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"made an assault"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"attack, upon him in war,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"battle."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b18-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hamalotu EalaY baniY fulaAnK","text_ar":"حَمَلْتُ عَلَى بَنِى فُلَانٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I made mischief,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I excited disorder, disagreement, dissension,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"strife, between,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"among, the sons of such a one."},{"kind":"text","text":"(AZ, S.) ―         -b19-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hamalahu EalaY AlA^amori","text_ar":"حَمَلَهُ عَلَى الاَمْرِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He incited, excited, urged, instigated, induced,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"made, him to do the thing,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"affair."},{"kind":"text","text":"(ISd, K.) ―         -b20-  ["},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hamala lafoZFA EalaY lafoZK A=xara","text_ar":"حَمَلَ لَفْظًا عَلَى لَفْظٍ ا=خَرَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HamolN","text_ar":"حَمْلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", a phrase often used in lexicology and grammar, (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He made,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"held, a word,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an expression, to accord in form,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in meaning,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"syntactically, with another word,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"expression."},{"kind":"text","text":"One says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yuHomalu EalaY AlA^akovari","text_ar":"يُحْمَلُ عَلَى الاَكْثَرِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a word)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"is made to accord in form with"},{"kind":"text","text":"those words with which it may be compared that constitute"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the greater number:"},{"kind":"text","text":"thus one says of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raHomaAnu","text_ar":"رَحْمَانُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", which is made to accord in form with words of the measure"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faEolaAnu","text_ar":"فَعْلَانُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", though it has not a fem. of the measure"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faEolaY","text_ar":"فَعْلَى"},{"kind":"text","text":", in preference to"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faEolaAnN","text_ar":"فَعْلَانٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", because words of the measure"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faEolaAnu","text_ar":"فَعْلَانُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"are more numerous than those of the measure"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faEolaAnN","text_ar":"فَعْلَانٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yuHomalu","text_ar":"يُحْمَلُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EalaY naqiyDihi","text_ar":"عَلَى نَقِيضِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a word)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"is made to accord in form with its contrary in meaning:"},{"kind":"text","text":"thus"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EijaAfN","text_ar":"عِجَافٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", an anomalous pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aEoHafu","text_ar":"اَعْحَفُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", is made to accord. in form with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"simaAnN","text_ar":"سِمَانٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", a regular pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"samiynN","text_ar":"سَمِينٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yaHmalu EalaY AlmaEonaY","text_ar":"يَحمَلُ عَلَى المَعْنَى"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a word)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"is made to accord syntactically with its meaning:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yuHomalu EalaY","text_ar":"يُحْمَلُ عَلَى"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"All~afoZi","text_ar":"اللَّفْظِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It is made to accord syntactically with its grammatical character:"},{"kind":"text","text":"the former is said when, in a sentence, we make a mase. word fem., and the contrary, because the meaning allows us to substitute a fem. syn. for the masc. word, and a masc. syn. for the fem. word: for ex., it is said in the Kur vi. 78,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"falam~aA raA^aY Al$~amosa baAzigapF qaAla h`*aA","text_ar":"فَلَمَّا رَاَى الشَّمْسَ بَازِغَةً قَالَ هٰذَا"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rab~iY","text_ar":"رَبِّى"},{"kind":"text","text":"“ And when he saw the sun rising, he said, This is my Lord: ” here (by saying"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bAzgp","text_ar":"بازغة"},{"kind":"text","text":")"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Al$ms","text_ar":"الشمس"},{"kind":"text","text":"is first made to accord syntactically with its grammatical character ("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tuHomalu EalaY All~afoZi","text_ar":"تُحْمَلُ عَلَى اللَّفْظِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"); and then (by saying"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"h`*aA","text_ar":"هٰذَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"instead of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"h`*ihi","text_ar":"هٰذِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":") it is made to accord syntactically with its meaning ("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tuHomalu EalaY","text_ar":"تُحْمَلُ عَلَى"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlmaEonaY","text_ar":"المَعْنَى"},{"kind":"text","text":"), which is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Aljirom","text_ar":"الجِرْم"},{"kind":"text","text":"or the like: this is allowable; but the reverse in respect of order is of weak authority; because the meaning is of more importance than the grammatical character of the word. (Collected from the Kull pp. 156 and 157, and other works.)] ―         -b21-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hamalahu A^aHosana maHoyalK","text_ar":"حَمَلَهُ اَحْسَنَ مَحْيَلٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He put the best construction upon it;"},{"kind":"text","text":"namely, a saying:"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mHml","text_ar":"محمل"},{"kind":"text","text":"being here an inf. n.]. (TA in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Abw","text_ar":"ابو"},{"kind":"text","text":") ―         -b22-  ["},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hamalahu EalaY Aln~aAsixi","text_ar":"حَمَلَهُ عَلَى النَّاسِخِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He attributed it to,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"charged it upon, the copyist;"},{"kind":"text","text":"namely, a mistake."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Humila ElaY Aln~aAsixi","text_ar":"حُمِلَ علَى النَّاسِخِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", said of a mistake, occurs in the K in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rbx","text_ar":"ربخ"},{"kind":"text","text":"―         -b23-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EalaY A=xara Hamala $ayoy^FA","text_ar":"عَلَى ا=خَرَ حَمَلَ شَيْيًا"},{"kind":"text","text":", in logic, means (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He predicated a thing of another"},{"kind":"text","text":"thing.] ―         -b24-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HumolaAnN","text_ar":"حُمْلَانٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":["Mgh","K","MA","S","Msb","TA","Az","T"]},{"entry_id":"n9173","headword_ar":"حَمْلَةٌ","root":"Hml","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A charge,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an assault"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"attack, in war,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"battle."},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, K.)"}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n9174","headword_ar":"حُمْلَةٌ","root":"Hml","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see what next follows."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n9175","headword_ar":"حِمْلَةٌ","root":"Hml","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HumolapN","text_ar":"حُمْلَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Carriage from one"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dAr","text_ar":"دار"},{"kind":"text","text":"[app. here meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"country,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"town,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the like,"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to another."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.)"}],"source_refs":[]}]}}